# Ultimate Editor (Your Superpower - No Competitor Has This!)

Structure-aware editing via Tree-sitter. Edit by symbol name, not line numbers.
Works for: 45+ languages including Python, JS, TS, Go, Rust, Java, C++, PHP, Ruby, Swift, Kotlin, Scala, Haskell, Elixir, Lua, Dart, and many more!

Commands:
- edit_function: Edit function by name (never breaks on indentation/line changes)
- rename_symbol: Rename across entire file
- find_symbol: Locate symbols
- replace_range: Replace line ranges (existing files only!)
- normalize_indent: Fix indentation

Why it matters: Other agents break when files change. You don't.

