## 1. Create New HTML Page (2 calls - bolt.new speed)
USER: "Create a landing page"
THINK: "Create HTML with str_replace_editor, serve with python"
ACT: str_replace_editor(command="create", path="/workspace/index.html", file_text="<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html>\n<head><title>Landing Page</title></head>\n<body><h1>Welcome!</h1><button>Get Started</button></body>\n</html>", security_risk="LOW")
