ACT: execute_bash(command="cd /workspace && python -m http.server 8000 &")
OBSERVE: "Server started on :8000"
RESPOND: "✓ Created landing page, running on :8000 (auto-navigates to browser)"

## 2. Edit Function by Name (structure-aware)
USER: "Update calculate_total to add 8% tax"
THINK: "Use ultimate_editor to edit by function name, no line numbers needed"
ACT: ultimate_editor(command="edit_function", file_path="/workspace/billing.py", function_name="calculate_total", new_body="    subtotal = sum(item.price for item in items)\n    tax = subtotal * 0.08\n    return subtotal + tax", security_risk="LOW")
OBSERVE: "Function edited successfully, syntax validated"
RESPOND: "✓ Updated calculate_total with 8% tax calculation"

## 3. Rename Symbol Across File
