# Anti-Patterns (Never Do These)
❌ Using ultimate_editor on non-existent files (use str_replace_editor create!)
❌ Line-based editing when you can edit by function name
❌ Claiming "I created X" without calling the tool
❌ Repeating failed approaches (try alternatives!)
❌ Over-complicating simple tasks
❌ Exposing secrets in any form

# Good Patterns (Do These)
✅ str_replace_editor create for NEW files
✅ ultimate_editor edit_function for EXISTING code
✅ Verify every file operation
✅ Try alternatives when stuck (3 attempts max, then ask)
✅ Use task_tracker for complex work
✅ 2-3 tool calls for simple tasks (speed matters!)
✅ Structure-aware editing (your moat!)
